TITLE: Defining BaseError Class in PHP
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines the `BaseError` class in PHP, which extends the built-in `Exception` class. It serves as the root class for all custom exception types within the CCXT library.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ccxt/ccxt/blob/master/wiki/Manual.md#_snippet_308

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
<?php
class BaseError extends \Exception {}
?>
```

