TITLE: Fetching Mark, Index OHLCV Data - JavaScript (Convenience Methods)
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet shows the use of convenience methods `fetchMarkOHLCV` and `fetchIndexOHLCV` to retrieve Mark and Index OHLCV data from an exchange. It assumes the ccxt library is installed and configured.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ccxt/ccxt/blob/master/wiki/Manual.md#_snippet_100

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
async function main () {
    const exchange = new ccxt.binanceusdm ()
    const markKlines = await exchange.fetchMarkOHLCV ('ADA/USDT', '1h')
    console.log (markKlines)
    const indexKlines = await exchange.fetchIndexOHLCV ('ADA/USDT', '1h')
    console.log (indexKlines)
}

main ()
```

