TITLE: Fetching Index OHLCV Data - Python
DESCRIPTION: This Python example demonstrates fetching Index OHLCV data using `fetch_ohlcv` and convenience methods `fetch_mark_ohlcv` and `fetch_index_ohlcv`. It uses the `ccxt` library and the `pprint` function for formatted output.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ccxt/ccxt/blob/master/wiki/Manual.md#_snippet_101

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
exchange = ccxt.binance()
response = exchange.fetch_ohlcv('ADA/USDT', '1h', params={'price':'index'})
pprint(response)
