TITLE: Creating a Market Buy Order with Price Specification in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating a market buy order when the exchange requires price specification. This uses the default option 'createMarketBuyOrderRequiresPrice' set to true, which calculates the total cost as amount * price.
