TITLE: Reloading Market Data with Force Reload (Python)
DESCRIPTION: This Python code snippet demonstrates how to load market data from the Poloniex exchange using the CCXT library. It initializes the exchange, loads markets, displays market information, and then forces a reload of the market data using the `load_markets(True)` method.  This method bypasses the cache and fetches fresh data from the exchange's API. The verbose mode is enabled to log HTTP requests.
