DESCRIPTION: Examples of different ways to configure custom nonce values in JavaScript, including constructor parameters, explicit redefinition, and using milliseconds-based nonce.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ccxt/ccxt/blob/master/doc/manual.rst#2025-04-22_snippet_99

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// JavaScript

